# Rule Generator

This rule enables the creation and updating of additional Cursor rules from conversations.

## Rule Creation Guidelines

When generating a new rule:
- Always begin the file with proper frontmatter
- Include a clear description
- Use appropriate globs for file patterns
- Format the rule content to be readable and concise

## Rule Structure

```
---
description: <Clear, concise description of what this rule does>
globs: <File patterns this rule applies to>
---

# <Rule Title>

<Rule content goes here>
```

## Common Rule Types

- **Always Applied**: These rules are always included
- **Auto Attached**: Included when files matching a glob pattern are referenced
- **Agent Requested**: Available to the AI, which decides whether to include based on the description
- **Manual**: Only included when explicitly mentioned using @ruleName
